</p>

<p>
<s>1. <phoneme alphabet="ipa" ph="ňĆ√¶d.o äňąna…™">Adonai</phoneme><break time="400ms"/> <emphasis level="moderate">Lord</emphasis>,<break time="400ms"/> Master.</s>
<break time="300ms"/>
<s>2. <phoneme alphabet="ipa" ph="…õl …õlňąjo än">El Elyon</phoneme><break time="400ms"/> The Most High <emphasis level="strong">God</emphasis>.</s>
