<s>4. <phoneme alphabet="ipa" ph="…õl  É√¶ňąda…™">El Shaddai</phoneme><break time="400ms"/> <emphasis level="strong">Lord</emphasis> <emphasis level="strong">God</emphasis> Almighty.</s>
<break time="300ms"/>
<s>5. <phoneme alphabet="ipa" ph="ňĆ…õl.o äňąhiňźm">Elohim</phoneme><break time="400ms"/> <emphasis level="strong">God</emphasis>.</s>
<break time="300ms"/>
<s>6. <phoneme alphabet="ipa" ph="d í…™ňąho ä.v…ô">Jehovah</phoneme> <phoneme alphabet="ipa" ph="ňąd ía…™.r…ô">Jireh</phoneme><break time="400ms"/> The <emphasis level="strong">Lord</emphasis> Will Provide.</s>
<break time="300ms"/>
<s>7. <phoneme alphabet="ipa" ph="d í…™ňąho ä.v…ô">Jehovah</phoneme> <phoneme alphabet="ipa" ph="m…õňąk…íd.…™ É.k…õm">Mekoddishkem</phoneme><break time="400ms"/> The <emphasis level="strong">Lord</emphasis> Who Sanctifies You.</s>
<break time="300ms"/>
<s>8. <phoneme alphabet="ipa" ph="d í…™ňąho ä.v…ô">Jehovah</phoneme> <phoneme alphabet="ipa" ph="ňąn…™s.iňź">Nissi</phoneme><break time="400ms"/> The <emphasis level="strong">Lord</emphasis> My Banner.</s>
<break time="300ms"/>
<s>9. <phoneme alphabet="ipa" ph="d í…™ňąho ä.v…ô">Jehovah</phoneme> <phoneme alphabet="ipa" ph="ňąr…Ďňź.f…ô">Rapha</phoneme><break time="400ms"/> The <emphasis level="strong">Lord</emphasis> That Heals.</s>
<break time="300ms"/>
<s>10. <phoneme alphabet="ipa" ph="d í…™ňąho ä.v…ô">Jehovah</phoneme> <phoneme alphabet="ipa" ph="ňąs√¶b.e…™.…íőł">Sabaoth</phoneme><break time="400ms"/> The <emphasis level="strong">Lord</emphasis> of Hosts.</s>
<break time="300ms"/>
<s>11. <phoneme alphabet="ipa" ph="d í…™ňąho ä.v…ô">Jehovah</phoneme> <phoneme alphabet="ipa" ph=" É…Ďňźňąlo äm">Shalom</phoneme><break time="400ms"/> The <emphasis level="strong">Lord</emphasis> Is Peace.</s>
<break time="300ms"/>
<s>12. <phoneme alphabet="ipa" ph="d í…™ňąho ä.v…ô">Jehovah</phoneme> <phoneme alphabet="ipa" ph="ňą É√¶m.…ô">Shammah</phoneme><break time="400ms"/> The <emphasis level="strong">Lord</emphasis> Is There.</s>
<break time="300ms"/>
<s>13. <phoneme alphabet="ipa" ph="d í…™ňąho ä.v…ô">Jehovah</phoneme> <phoneme alphabet="ipa" ph="ts…™dňąke…™.nuňź">Tsidkenu</phoneme><break time="400ms"/> The <emphasis level="strong">Lord</emphasis> Our Righteousness.</s>
